								</table>

								<p class="h_services">This office heads the following services:</p>
								
								<div id="h_STSRO-DTB">
								<p><a href="javascript:ShowHide('STSRO-DTB')">Direct Taxes Branch</a></p>
								</div>
								<div id="STSRO-DTB" class="iL2">
								<p class="OfficeDesc">This Branch specifically handles the conduct of studies on: individual and corporate income taxation; transfer taxes; and other direct taxes. As such, it prepares estimates of the impact of tax measures on government revenue and on the tax burden of corporate and individual income taxpayers, as the case may be. Generally, it liaises with government agencies especially the Department of Finance (DOF), particularly with the Bureau of Internal Revenue (BIR) and the National Tax Research Center (NTRC) as well as with the Land Transportation Office (LTO), among others, and the private sector in the formulation and evaluation of pertinent tax proposals, and thereby prepares position papers, briefers and/or draft bills/amendments on subject tax matters.</p>
