								<div id="h_STSRO-ITB">
								<p><a href="javascript:ShowHide('STSRO-ITB')">Indirect Taxes Branch</a></p>
								</div>
								<div id="STSRO-ITB" class="iL2">
								<p class="OfficeDesc">This Branch specifically focuses on indirect taxes such as the value-added, excise, documentary stamp and other percentage taxes. Generally, it liaises with government agencies especially the Department of Finance (DOF), particularly with the Bureau of Internal Revenue (BIR), the Bureau of Customs (BoC), the National Tax Research Center (NTRC), and the private sector in the formulation and evaluation of pertinent indirect tax proposals, and thereby prepares studies, briefers, fiscal estimates and statistics as well as draft bills on indirect taxation.</p>
